title: Compressed square font help please?!
content:
Does anybody know what this is?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20130819000953im_/http:/typophile.com/files/evsdda_5474.jpg)

author: smallfish

comments.content:
It must be **[Ultra 911](http://web.archive.org/web/20130819000953/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-2&ffam=Ultra%20911%20-%20Regular&fid=3db7dbf7ca7339526e121e556a680a84&fsize=36&text=EVSO%20DIGITAL%20AUDIO&wrap=2)** by Iconian Fonts (2003, free for personal use)

------------------  
I found it using "Find my Font": [http://www.findmyfont.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20130819000953/http:/www.findmyfont.com/ "http://www.findmyfont.com")
That's it! Thanks, I was looking for ages!
